{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_02_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 四人でLizNoir",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4、5……\nここの動きはもっとおっきく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4‚ 5…\nI need to go bigger here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3066.6666666666674,
          "startTime": 8.266666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、愛。今日も朝早くから振り付けの練習か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning‚ Ai. Practicing first thing in the morning?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "今日は夕方からお仕事があるので\n午前中に練習しようと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to work this evening‚\nso I wanted to practice during the daytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日も夜遅くまで練習してたんだろ？\nあまり無理しないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were already practicing until late last night.\nPlease‚ don’t push yourself too hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、分かりました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood! I’ll be careful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-evening",
      "startTime": 30.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4、5……\nしっくりこないなぁ……もう一回最初から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4‚ 5…\nThat still doesn’t feel right. Again‚ from the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4200.000000000003,
          "startTime": 41.86666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}. Is it that time already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "も、もしかして朝からずっと踊り続けてたのか\nもう夕方だぞ。少し休憩した方がいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-have you been dancing since morning?\nIt’s evening! Maybe you should take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もうすぐ仕事に行かないといけないので\nそれまでは練習させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s almost time to go to work.\nLet me practice until then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "よし、もう一度頭から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once more‚ from the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ、まいったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I need to stage an intervention?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4633.33333333334,
          "startTime": 69.13333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-night",
      "startTime": 68.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにこの時間になると誰も残っていないな\n夜も遅いし、愛ももう帰っただろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no one left now‚ surely.\nI’m sure Ai wouldn’t be here this late…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　まだいたのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What! You’re still here?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、仕事が予定より早く終わったので\n戻ってずっと練習してました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I finished work early so I came back\nto get some more practice in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "まだまだ完璧とは言えないので\n今夜は納得がいくまで居残り練習するつもりです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still haven’t perfected it yet‚\nso I’m not stopping tonight until I get it done!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いくらなんでも根を詰め過ぎだ\nまぁ、そんな不器用な所が愛らしいとも言えるが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now you’re definitely overdoing it.\nAlthough it’s just like you‚ Ai‚ to push yourself too hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ前に体を壊したらどうする気だ\n無理はせずに今日はもう帰ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don’t need you collapsing before the concert.\nJust take the night off. Relax.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました……\nじゃあ、明日は朝から練習するということで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. I understand.\nI’ll get back to it first thing in the morning tomorrow――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ。明日は練習を中止して俺に付き合ってくれ\nいいな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope. No training tomorrow either. You’re going out with me.\nUnderstand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　お、俺と、つ、付き合え！　って！\nそんな急に、大胆な……私、困ります……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What! Go out… w-with you?!\nThis is all so sudden! I’m not sure what to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "違う、違う。聞き間違いだよ\n気晴らしをするって話だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ no. That’s not what I meant.\nI’m just saying you need to unwind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁんだ、びっくりした\n口から心臓が飛び出ちゃいそうでしたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ okay. That was a shock.\nI thought my heart was going to explode!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "今日は会場の下見に付き合ってもらったが\nステージを見てどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that we’ve checked out the venue together today‚\nhow did you feel seeing the stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.33333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "はい、最近は振り付けのことばかり考えていたので\nいい気分転換になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My head has been full of dance moves recently\nso it was a nice change of pace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐライブだが結果は出せそうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The concert is soon. Will you be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
